# ============ ML artifacts (large files — use S3 instead) ============
# Bulk data: produced, generated, or cached. Source of truth is S3.
data/raw/**
data/processed/**
data/cache/**
# Tiny committed sample sets under data/sft/ and data/dpo/ are kept in git
# for smoke tests and onboarding. Real datasets (v1+) live in S3 and are
# referenced from data/dataset_info.json via s3:// URLs.
!data/**/.gitkeep

